52:28.834 --> 52:33.172
I guess I'd grab a tree
or branch or something

52:33.255 --> 52:35.132
to stay connected to the earth.

52:35.466 --> 52:39.011
You know, so I wouldn't go floating
up into space!

52:43.224 --> 52:44.767
I don't think I'd grab on.

52:46.769 --> 52:48.145
I'd go.

52:56.904 --> 52:58.948
[radio chatter]

52:59.031 --> 53:02.076
[distant siren]

53:09.500 --> 53:10.626
[knock on door]

53:12.086 --> 53:13.504
Mrs. Ford?

53:14.255 --> 53:17.133
I'm Louisa Kinnie,
I'm with Child Protective Services.

53:17.216 --> 53:18.509
