to help me find my kid.

53:22.680 --> 53:24.098
Is this a joke?

53:24.932 --> 53:26.017
May I come in?

53:35.109 --> 53:36.402
This is quite a collection.

53:36.902 --> 53:38.904
- She loved to dress up.
- Hmm!

53:42.158 --> 53:43.951
And that's quite a collection as well.

53:48.164 --> 53:50.332
I'm the mother, not a suspect.

53:50.875 --> 53:52.168
Unfortunately, Mrs. Ford,

53:52.251 --> 53:54.670
we need to consider all possibilities.

53:54.754 --> 53:56.005
It's my job to determine

53:56.088 --> 53:59.008
how you planned
for the safety of this child.

54:03.054 --> 54:04.555
Is that your first kid?

54:06.182 --> 54:08.851
No, it's my third.

54:10.770 --> 54:12.271
Imagine losing one.

54:15.441 --> 54:16.609
I can't.

54:20.988 --> 54:22.031
[Manuel] No, no!

54:22.114 --> 54:24.450
Hey, let me help you, Mrs. Mooney.

54:24.533 --> 54:25.659
Thank you!

54:26.243 --> 54:27.745
There you go!

54:29.747 --> 54:31.040
You got a baby, Mrs. Mooney?

54:31.123 --> 54:33.125
No! I have a...

54:33.209 --> 54:35.628
