55:32.726 --> 55:35.271
No! Absolutely not!

55:35.354 --> 55:36.981
My God! My furniture!

55:37.064 --> 55:38.315
What have you done?

55:38.399 --> 55:39.859
I put out newspapers.

55:39.942 --> 55:41.402
No! These are my things.

55:41.485 --> 55:42.903
You have no right to touch them.

55:43.195 --> 55:45.114
I just thought it would be fun, and...

55:45.364 --> 55:47.324
Who does that? What's wrong with you?

55:47.950 --> 55:49.869
Pfft! A lot? [scoffs]

55:50.578 --> 55:52.913
This is my home, it's not a joke.

55:52.997 --> 55:53.831
[Tallulah] Okay.

55:53.914 --> 55:56.458
God, this is a 1920s Soumak carpet.

55:56.542 --> 55:59.170
You can't just do anything you want.

55:59.253 --> 56:01.755
- I just thought that you...
- Don't! stop it!

56:01.839 --> 56:03.424
Stop. You don't know what I want.

56:03.507 --> 56:06.969
You're... like a feral beast.

56:07.052 --> 56:09.889
- I don't know what I was thinking.
- These things aren't even yours.

56:09.972 --> 56:12.224
Don't do that! I took you in.

56:12.308 --> 56:13.809
I will not be taken advantage of.

56:13.893 --> 56:15.102
It's not personal, Margo.

56:15.186 --> 56:16.520
