56:16.604 --> 56:18.898
Get your filthy fingers off of that.

56:18.981 --> 56:22.568
I will not let some crazy kid come in

56:22.651 --> 56:25.321
and destroy my life for her own amusement.

56:25.404 --> 56:26.947
Jesus!

56:28.115 --> 56:29.450
