56:31.744 --> 56:33.287
I need you to go.

56:33.871 --> 56:35.748
- Are you serious?
- Of course I'm serious.

56:35.831 --> 56:37.499
Get out! Go live in your van.

56:37.583 --> 56:39.919
You can paint any goddamn thing you want.

56:40.002 --> 56:45.174
This is where I live! This is my space!
I have things the way I want them!

56:45.257 --> 56:47.676
Do you understand? This is how I like it!

56:48.093 --> 56:48.969
