57:04.652 --> 57:05.652
[sighs]

57:16.747 --> 57:19.959
See? Now it's yours.

57:25.422 --> 57:27.258
I've done crazy things.

57:27.633 --> 57:28.842
Sure.

57:29.927 --> 57:30.927
