57:30.970 --> 57:33.764
- I mean, I bet I can beat it, but...
- Mm-hmm.

57:33.847 --> 57:35.641
[news program playing on TV]

57:37.810 --> 57:40.312
I smuggled heroin in my crotch.

57:40.854 --> 57:41.981
No, you didn't.

57:42.982 --> 57:44.525
- Sort of.
- How do you sort of...

57:44.608 --> 57:46.235
smuggle heroin in your crotch?

57:46.318 --> 57:49.405
I had a boyfriend, we were madly in love,

57:49.488 --> 57:52.241
he was in a terrible
rock band, he was so...

57:53.617 --> 57:55.369
sexy!

57:56.870 --> 57:59.206
And we were coming back
from a trip to India...

57:59.290 --> 58:00.416
Oh my God, I wanna go!

58:00.499 --> 58:02.084
Don't, it's horrible!

58:02.167 --> 58:04.253
Dead cows floating down the same river

58:04.336 --> 58:07.006
people drink out of.
It's horr... dirty, dirty.

58:08.757 --> 58:11.885
I made it as far as the airport bathroom.

58:11.969 --> 58:13.512
And?

58:14.471 --> 58:16.432
I couldn't stick it up there.

58:16.765 --> 58:18.142
I panicked. I left it on the sink.

58:18.434 --> 58:19.578
And what happened to the guy?

58:19.602 --> 58:21.520
He was furious,
he dumped me after that trip.

58:21.604 --> 58:23.564
I was just too much of
a goody two-shoes.

58:23.647 --> 58:25.149
You need to tell Nico this story,

58:25.232 --> 58:27.401
because he thinks you're such a tight ass.

58:31.030 --> 58:32.323
Is that why he left?

58:32.865 --> 58:35.618
I don't know.
He said something like...

58:35.701 --> 58:38.829
"I'm her son, I'm not her husband."

58:41.081 --> 58:44.209
Well, my God! I know that.

58:47.630 --> 58:49.149
[news program] <i>Madison has blond hair...</i>

58:49.173 --> 58:51.884
<i>and blue eyes.
The suspect is a woman...</i>

58:51.967 --> 58:54.720
[Margo] Did he use that word, "tight ass"?

58:57.222 --> 58:59.016
Christ! Well, you know what,

58:59.099 --> 59:01.477
