really far into the future,

01:08:51.649 --> 01:08:53.443
but still she's...

01:08:55.069 --> 01:08:58.907
she's gonna die and that... makes me sad.

01:08:58.990 --> 01:08:59.908
Oh, we're all gonna die.

01:08:59.991 --> 01:09:02.911
