and I'll be sad or,

01:09:19.886 --> 01:09:22.055
I'll die first and you'll be sad.

01:09:25.015 --> 01:09:26.434
Either way,

01:09:28.853 --> 01:09:30.313
we're all gonna be dead.

01:09:35.359 --> 01:09:38.697
[laughter]

01:09:38.779 --> 01:09:42.575
- It's so fucking sad!
- It's the saddest thing ever!

01:09:42.658 --> 01:09:43.993
- So sad!
- So sad!

01:09:44.077 --> 01:09:45.996
