- [horn blares]
- [Tallulah] Shit!

01:26:10.604 --> 01:26:12.439
Oh, fuck!

01:26:12.523 --> 01:26:14.191
Okay, all right.

01:26:14.275 --> 01:26:15.818
I'm gonna get you some medicine.

01:26:15.901 --> 01:26:17.903
- [baby crying]
- You're gonna be okay.

01:26:17.987 --> 01:26:21.490
Okay. Okay. Okay.

