01:26:42.219 --> 01:26:44.305
You were drunk, Carolyn?

01:27:13.959 --> 01:27:15.377
Hi, Mom.

01:27:17.629 --> 01:27:18.629
Hi!

01:27:22.134 --> 01:27:23.969
