01:31:19.496 --> 01:31:21.832
If you take her there,
then you are done, that is it.

01:31:21.915 --> 01:31:22.915
They have you!

01:31:23.917 --> 01:31:25.002
Shh!

01:31:25.877 --> 01:31:26.878
