that's the only reason I did it.

01:38:13.118 --> 01:38:14.536
Where are you going?

01:38:15.412 --> 01:38:17.789
- I'm sorry <i>.</i>
- [Margo] <i>Lu?</i>

01:38:23.920 --> 01:38:26.548
Okay. We got her.
Let's get somebody over there now.

01:39:21.144 --> 01:39:24.189
[baby screaming]

01:39:32.280 --> 01:39:33.615
