01:39:39.329 --> 01:39:42.123
[whispers] It's okay, it's okay.

01:39:43.500 --> 01:39:46.711
It's okay. It's okay.

01:39:47.420 --> 01:39:48.588
I got you.

01:39:48.922 --> 01:39:49.756
